#. <html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta content="Pali text from the Mahāsaṅgīti Tipiṭaka Buddhavasse 2500" name="description"><title></title></head><body><div id="text" lang="pli"><section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs0.3"
msgid "Aniyatakaṇḍa"
msgstr "Monks’ Undetermined"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs0.4"
msgid "2. Dutiyaaniyatasikkhāpada"
msgstr "2. The second training rule"

#. </h1></div><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.336"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-an.2.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1829"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī—“bhagavatā paṭikkhittaṃ mātugāmena "
"saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappetun”ti "
"tassāyeva kumārikāya saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ kappesi kālayuttaṃ "
"samullapanto kālayuttaṃ dhammaṃ bhaṇanto."
msgstr ""
"At this time Venerable Udāyī knew that the Master had prohibited sitting "
"alone with a woman on a private and concealed seat suitable for doing it, "
"and so instead he sat alone in private with the same girl. When they were "
"able, they just chatted; otherwise he gave her a teaching."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.3"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho visākhā migāramātā nimantitā taṃ kulaṃ agamāsi."
msgstr "A second time Visākhā had been invited to that family."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.4"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho visākhā migāramātā āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ tassāyeva kumārikāya saddhiṃ "
"ekaṃ ekāya raho nisinnaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When she arrived, she saw Udāyī sitting alone in private with the same girl,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.5"
msgid "Disvāna āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "and she said to Udāyī,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.6"
msgid ""
"“idaṃ, bhante, nacchannaṃ nappatirūpaṃ yaṃ ayyo mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya "
"raho nisajjaṃ kappeti."
msgstr ""
"“Venerable, it’s not appropriate that you should sit alone with a woman on a "
"private seat."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.7"
msgid ""
"Kiñcāpi, bhante, ayyo anatthiko tena dhammena, api ca dussaddhāpayā "
"appasannā manussā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Although you may not be aiming at that act, people with little confidence "
"are hard to convince.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.8"
msgid "Evampi kho āyasmā udāyī visākhāya migāramātuyā vuccamāno nādiyi."
msgstr "But Udāyī did not listen."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.9"
msgid "Atha kho visākhā migāramātā nikkhamitvā bhikkhūnaṃ etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "After leaving, Visākhā told the monks about what had happened."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.10"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.11"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.12"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma āyasmā udāyī mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ "
"kappessatī”ti."
msgstr "“How can Venerable Udāyī sit alone with a woman on a private seat?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1830"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.13"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā bhagavato "
"etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After rebuking Udāyī in many ways, they told the Master …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.14"
msgid ""
"“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, udāyi, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ "
"kappesī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, Udāyī, that you sat alone with a woman on a private seat?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.15"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.16"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.17"
msgid ""
"kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ "
"kappessasi."
msgstr "Foolish man, how can you sit alone with a woman on a private seat?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.18"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.19"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.19a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.192"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1831"></a>
#. <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.20"
msgid ""
"“Na heva kho pana paṭicchannaṃ āsanaṃ hoti nālaṅkammaniyaṃ, alañca kho hoti "
"mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsituṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘Although a seat is not concealed, nor suitable for doing it, it may be "
"suitable for speaking lewdly to a woman."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.337"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.21"
msgid ""
"Yo pana bhikkhu tathārūpe āsane mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ "
"kappeyya, tamenaṃ saddheyyavacasā upāsikā disvā dvinnaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena "
"vadeyya—"
msgstr ""
"If a monk sits alone with a woman in private on such a seat, and a "
"trustworthy female lay follower sees him and accuses him of"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.22"
msgid "saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "an offense entailing suspension or an offense entailing confession,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.23"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ bhikkhu paṭijānamāno dvinnaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena kāretabbo—"
msgstr "then, if he admits to the sitting, he is be dealt with"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.24"
msgid "saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "according to one of these two"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.25"
msgid "Yena vā sā saddheyyavacasā upāsikā vadeyya tena so bhikkhu kāretabbo."
msgstr "or according to what that trustworthy female lay follower has said."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.26"
msgid "Ayampi dhammo aniyato”ti."
msgstr "This rule too is undetermined.’”"

#. </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs1.27"
msgid "(<em>2</em>:<strong>19</strong>)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-an.2.2"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-an.2.2.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1832"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.1"
msgid "Na heva kho pana paṭicchannaṃ āsanaṃ hotīti"
msgstr "Although a seat is not concealed:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.2"
msgid ""
"appaṭicchannaṃ hoti kuṭṭena vā kavāṭena vā kilañjena vā sāṇipākārena vā "
"rukkhena vā thambhena vā kotthaḷiyā vā yena kenaci appaṭicchannaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"it is not concealed by a wall, a screen, a door, a screening cloth, a tree, "
"a pillar, a grain container, or anything else."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1833"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.3"
msgid "Nālaṅkammaniyanti"
msgstr "Nor suitable for doing it:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.4"
msgid "na sakkā hoti methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevituṃ."
msgstr "one is not able to have sexual intercourse."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1834"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.5"
msgid "Alañca kho hoti mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsitunti"
msgstr "It may be suitable for speaking lewdly to a woman:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.6"
msgid "sakkā hoti mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsituṃ."
msgstr "one is able to speak lewdly to a woman."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1835"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.7"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.8"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.9"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.10"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""
"… The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order "
"through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is "
"unchallengeable and fit to stand—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.11"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1836"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.12"
msgid "Tathārūpe āsaneti"
msgstr "On such a seat:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.13"
msgid "evarūpe āsane."
msgstr "on that sort of seat."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1837"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.14"
msgid "Mātugāmo nāma"
msgstr "A woman:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.15"
msgid "manussitthī, na yakkhī na petī na tiracchānagatā,"
msgstr ""
"a human female, not a female spirit, not a female ghost, not a female animal."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.16"
msgid "viññū paṭibalā subhāsitadubbhāsitaṃ duṭṭhullāduṭṭhullaṃ ājānituṃ."
msgstr ""
"She understands and is capable of discerning bad speech and good speech, "
"what is lewd and what is not lewd."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1838"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.17"
msgid "Saddhinti"
msgstr "With:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.18"
msgid "ekato."
msgstr "together."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1839"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.19"
msgid "Eko ekāyāti"
msgstr "Alone:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.20"
msgid "bhikkhu ceva hoti mātugāmo ca."
msgstr "just the monk and the woman."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1840"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.21"
msgid "Raho nāma"
msgstr "Private:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.22"
msgid "cakkhussa raho, sotassa raho."
msgstr "there is private to the eye and there is private to the ear."

#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.23"
msgid "Cakkhussa raho nāma"
msgstr "Private to the eye:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.24"
msgid ""
"na sakkā hoti akkhiṃ vā nikhaṇīyamāne bhamukaṃ vā ukkhipīyamāne sīsaṃ vā "
"ukkhipīyamāne passituṃ."
msgstr "one is unable to see them winking, raising an eyebrow, or nodding."

#. </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.25"
msgid "Sotassa raho nāma"
msgstr "Private to the ear:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.26"
msgid "na sakkā hoti pakatikathā sotuṃ."
msgstr "one is unable to hear ordinary speech."

#. </span></span></p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1841"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.27"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ kappeyyāti"
msgstr "Sits:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.28"
msgid "mātugāme nisinne bhikkhu upanisinno vā hoti upanipanno vā."
msgstr "the monk sits down or lies down next to the seated woman."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.29"
msgid "Bhikkhu nisinne mātugāmo upanisinno vā hoti upanipanno vā."
msgstr "The woman sits down or lies down next to the seated monk."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.30"
msgid "Ubho vā nisinnā honti ubho vā nipannā."
msgstr "Both are seated or both are lying down."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1842"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.31"
msgid "Saddheyyavacasā nāma"
msgstr "Trustworthy:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.32"
msgid "āgataphalā abhisametāvinī viññātasāsanā."
msgstr ""
"she has attained the fruit, she has broken through, she has understood the "
"Teaching."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1843"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.33"
msgid "Upāsikā nāma"
msgstr "Female lay follower:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.34"
msgid "buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, saṃghaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā."
msgstr "she has gone for refuge to the Buddha, the Teaching, and the Order."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1844"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.35"
msgid "Disvāti"
msgstr "Sees:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.1.36"
msgid "passitvā."
msgstr "having seen."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-an.2.2.2"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.338"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1845"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.1"
msgid "Dvinnaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena vadeyya saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr ""
"Accuses him of an offense entailing suspension or an offense entailing "
"confession,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.2"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ bhikkhu paṭijānamāno dvinnaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena kāretabbo—"
msgstr "then, if he admits to the sitting, he is be dealt with"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.3"
msgid "saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "according to one of these two"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.4"
msgid "Yena vā sā saddheyyavacasā upāsikā vadeyya, tena so bhikkhu kāretabbo."
msgstr "or according to what that trustworthy female lay follower has said:"

#. </span></p><div class="gloss"><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1846"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.5"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.6"
msgid ""
"“ayyo mayā diṭṭho nisinno mātugāmena saddhiṃ kāyasaṃsaggaṃ samāpajjanto”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you seated, making physical contact with a woman,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.7"
msgid "so ca taṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo."
msgstr "and he admits to that, then he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.8"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.9"
msgid ""
"“ayyo mayā diṭṭho nisinno mātugāmena saddhiṃ kāyasaṃsaggaṃ samāpajjanto”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you seated, making physical contact with a woman,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.10"
msgid "so ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "but he says,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.11"
msgid "“saccāhaṃ nisinno, no ca kho kāyasaṃsaggaṃ samāpajjin”ti,"
msgstr "“It’s true that I was seated, but I didn’t make physical contact,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.12"
msgid "nisajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the sitting. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.13"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nisinno, api ca kho nipanno”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but lying down,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.14"
msgid "nipajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the lying down. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.15"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nisinno, api ca kho ṭhito”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but standing,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.16"
msgid "na kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is not to be dealt with."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="19"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.193"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1847"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.17"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.18"
msgid ""
"“ayyo mayā diṭṭho nipanno mātugāmena saddhiṃ kāyasaṃsaggaṃ samāpajjanto”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you lying down, making physical contact with a woman,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.19"
msgid "so ca taṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "and he admits to that, then he is to be dealt with for the offense. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.20"
msgid "“saccāhaṃ nipanno, no ca kho kāyasaṃsaggaṃ samāpajjin”ti,"
msgstr "“It’s true that I was lying down, but I didn’t make physical contact,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.21"
msgid "nipajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the lying down. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.22"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nipanno, api ca kho nisinno”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t lying down, but seated,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.23"
msgid "nisajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the sitting. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.24"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nipanno, api ca kho ṭhito”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but standing,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.25"
msgid "na kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is not to be dealt with."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="20"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1848"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.26"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.27"
msgid ""
"“ayyassa mayā sutaṃ nisinnassa mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsantassā”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve heard you speaking lewdly to a woman while seated,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.28"
msgid "so ca taṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo."
msgstr "and he admits to that, then he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.29"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.30"
msgid ""
"“ayyassa mayā sutaṃ nisinnassa mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsantassā”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve heard you speaking lewdly to a woman while seated,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.31"
msgid "so ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "but he says,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.32"
msgid "“saccāhaṃ nisinno, no ca kho duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsin”ti,"
msgstr "“It’s true that I was seated, but I didn’t speak lewdly,”"

