msgstr "“I wasn’t lying down, but standing,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.60"
msgid "na kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is not to be dealt with."

#. </p></div><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1852"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.61"
msgid "Ayampīti"
msgstr "This rule too:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.62"
msgid "purimaṃ upādāya vuccati."
msgstr "this is said with reference to the previous undetermined rule."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="25"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1853"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.63"
msgid "Aniyatoti"
msgstr "Undetermined:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.64"
msgid "na niyato,"
msgstr "not determined."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs2.2.65"
msgid "saṃghādiseso vā pācittiyaṃ vā."
msgstr ""
"It is either an offense entailing suspension or an offense entailing "
"confession."

#. </span>
#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="26"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-an.2.3"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1854"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.1"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā "
"kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"If he admits to going, and he admits to sitting, and he admits to an "
"offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.2"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā "
"kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"If he admits to going, but he does not admit to sitting, yet he admits to an "
"offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.3"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, nisajjāya "
"kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"If he admits to going, and he admits to sitting, but he does not admit to an "
"offense, he is to be dealt with for the sitting."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.4"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, na "
"kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"If he admits to going, but he does not admit to sitting, nor does he admit "
"to an offense, he is not to be dealt with."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="27"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1855"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.5"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā "
"kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"If he does not admit to going, but he admits to sitting, and he admits to an "
"offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.6"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā "
"kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"If he does not admit to going, nor does he admit to sitting, but he admits "
"to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.7"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, nisajjāya "
"kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"If he does not admit to going, but he admits to sitting, yet he does not "
"admit to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the sitting."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.8"
msgid ""
"Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, na "
"kāretabboti."
msgstr ""
"If he does not admit to going, nor does he admit to sitting, nor does he "
"admit to an offense, he is not to be dealt with."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="28"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1856"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.9"
msgid "Dutiyo aniyato niṭṭhito."
msgstr "The second undetermined rule is finished."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="29"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.194"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.340"></a> <a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1857"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.10"
msgid "Uddiṭṭhā kho āyasmanto dve aniyatā dhammā."
msgstr "“Venerables, the two undetermined rules have been recited."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.11"
msgid "Tatthāyasmante pucchāmi—"
msgstr "In regard to this I ask you,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.12"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.13"
msgid "Dutiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A second time I ask,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.14"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.15"
msgid "Tatiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A third time I ask,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.16"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.17"
msgid "Parisuddhetthāyasmanto;"
msgstr "You are pure in this"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.18"
msgid "tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "and therefore silent."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.19"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmīti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection summary"><a class="sc" id="30"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1858"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.20"
msgid "Tassuddānaṃ"
msgstr "This is the summary:"

#. </p><div class="uddana"><p><a class="sc" id="31"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1859"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.21"
msgid "Alaṃ kammaniyañceva,"
msgstr "Suitable for doing it,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.22"
msgid "tatheva ca naheva kho;"
msgstr "And then not so;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.23"
msgid "Aniyatā supaññattā,"
msgstr "The undetermined rules have been well laid down"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.24"
msgid "buddhaseṭṭhena tādināti."
msgstr "By the Stable One, the Buddha who is the best."

#. </p></div><p class="endsection"><a class="sc" id="32"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1860"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:pts-cs3.25"
msgid "Aniyatakaṇḍaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The chapter on undetermined rules is finished."

